Yeah, my friend Slayn Alive >SP wanted me to make a map, so here I am. it started out a large arena, with a big wall and a hill to bomb, but it turns out the fort I built in the corner made me want to make a bunker =P. it's my first (successful)map, all my other maps were either too small, simple, or non-functional.
